sentences: Mikoi Sasaki (佐々木未来, Sasaki Mikoi, born March 30, 1991) is a Japanese voice actress known for her role as Hercule Barton in Tantei Opera Milky Holmes, and her other major roles include Himeno Katsuragi in Da Capo III, Kuguru Uki in Future Card Buddyfight, and Neko in Recently, My Sister Is Unusual.
In a video posted in October 2020, Sasaki and the two others stated that they wished for their YouTube channel to be detailed in their Wikipedia pages.

On April 10 2020, Sasaki, Aimi (actress) and Ayasa Itō started their own YouTube channel under the name of the Three Voice Acting Sisters [Team Y].
